Package com.hac.Exception

Class ErrorMessages

java.lang.Object
com.hac.Exception.ErrorMessages
public final class ErrorMessages extends Object
The ErrorMessages class is a utility class that contains constant strings for various error messages used throughout the application. These constants help to maintain consistency in error reporting and make it easier to update or modify error messages in the future.
